headline: 2 High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy in May and Hold Forever
summary: AbbVie has a rare dividend track record and impressive innovative abilities.  Gilead is a leader in its core market and increasingly growing a presence in others.  When investing in dividend stocks, paying attention to the right things is essential.
